structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
FINANCE AND REVENUE OF CITIES OTHER THAN THE FIRST CLASS

law.history: Repealed 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 434, sec. 15, effective July 15, 1982. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 384, sec. 217, effective June 17, 1978. -- Created 1968 Ky. Acts ch. 34, sec. 1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Map and statement showing taxes due, due date and collector filed with county clerk in fifth and sixth-class cities in county having first-class city.
